        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "w = \\frac 1 {4a} \\left[ 4a^2 \\left( x + \\frac b {2a}y \\right)^2  + (4ac - b^2)y^2 \\right]\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "3 cases:\n",
        "\n",
        "1) $4ac - b^2 < 0 \\Rightarrow$ saddle point.\n",
        "2) $4ac - b^2 = 0 \\Rightarrow$ degenerate critical point.\n",
        "3) $4ac - b^2 > 0$\n",
        "    $\\qquad\\rightarrow$ if $a > 0$ minimum.\n",
        "    $\\qquad\\rightarrow$ if $a < 0$ maximum.\n",
        "\n",
        "## General case\n",
